# Local Development Configuration
# 
# For .NET projects, use User Secrets instead of .env files:
#   cd src/ApimBilling.Api
#   dotnet user-secrets set "APIM_NAME" "your-apim-instance"
#   dotnet user-secrets set "APIM_RESOURCE_GROUP" "your-apim-resource-group"
#   dotnet user-secrets set "AZURE_SUBSCRIPTION_ID" "your-subscription-id"
#
# User secrets are stored outside your source code and won't be committed to Git.
#
# For Azure deployment, set these as App Service environment variables.
# For Bicep deployment, override parameters at deployment time:
#   az deployment group create --parameters apimName="your-apim" apimResourceGroup="your-rg"
